reviewText: This ends the Muramasa and personified zanpaktos story arc and returns to the main story. I have to assume you know what Bleach is if you are looking at volume 18, so I won't go into any more detail. I like this story arc more than some personally.
summary: Return to the main story line

reviewText: I enjoy  Bleach, however I found all the filler arches to be a waste of my time and money.  I know there are people that enjoy them however, I just don't see why they can't release these sets in groups that have filler only so they can be skipped by those that really don't care for it.Basically I'm going to be forced to get this set to get the one episode that really matters 267.  I know there is a recap episode of the cannon arch, but if you aren't watching a 40 episode filler that really isn't necessary.
summary: Really tired of box sets that combine filler and non-filler episodes
